            <mixed-citation publication-type="journal">Lindblad A, Hultcrantz R, Strandvik B. High doses of aminoglycosides did not produce liver toxicity in patients with cystic fibrosis. J Hepatol 1994; 20: 201-5. <annotation><p><italic toggle="yes">(Five patients with cystic fibrosis underwent yearly liver biopsies; those on intermittent aminoglycoside therapy showed no hepatic abnormalities and liver tests were normal in all).</italic></p></annotation><pub-id pub-id-type="pmid">8006400</pub-id></mixed-citation>
          </ref>
